snippet.title: Let's Play Empire Total War: Darthmod - United Provinces #1
snippet.description:
Hey guys hope you enjoy, bear in mind this is my first video of my first series so it's going to be  off to a bit of a rough start. Mainly me getting used to going this during a TW campaign, I know in places my voice volume seems to rise and fall a bit too much.

Anyway please enjoy, more videos to follow

Channel: http://bit.ly/1e7HY7e
United Provinces playlist:http://bit.ly/1felRHZ If you've got any questions or naming requests then make sure you post them in the comments section to make sure I get it!

Why not hit like, it lets me know what you guys enjoy so it'll help me figure out exactly the best way to entertain you.

Steam - http://steamcommunity.com/id/theriflemanuk
Twitter - https://twitter.com/theriflemanuk Please note this is an unofficial video and is not endorsed by SEGA or the Creative Assembly in any way.
